73.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hxk1665703198673.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hxk1665703198673.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hxk1665703198673\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Retrieves information to the USTATE table.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__topic_d135758e1_d135759e1_d135760e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__p_d135761e1_d135762e1_d135763e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">\"USYSSTAT\".GetState</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SesstionId</var>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">SessionData</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__section_N1003C_N10016_N10001\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__4\">Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SesstionId</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__4\">Generated by Uniface, and accessible using\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">$webinfo(\"WEBSERVERCONTEXT\"), SESSION</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__4\">Name of the server page component instance,\n                        returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SessionData</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__3\">OUT</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hxk1665703198673__table_d16250e1_d16251e1_d16252e1__entry__4\">Uniface list of state information.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__section_mgs_qbg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1224191e180\">Returns</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface list of state information.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__section_tbq_mmr_bdc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1224191e189\">Example: GetState</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__p_d135773e1_d135774e1_d135775e1\">The default code of the preActivate trigger of\n            dynamic and static server pages activates the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">GetState</span> operation and\n            use the information returned in <var class=\"keyword varname\">SessionData</var> to set component\n            variables to restore the server page state:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hxk1665703198673_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hxk1665703198673__codeblock_ovz_vbg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger preActivate\nvariables \n string WebServerContext, Session, UserContext\nendvariables\n WebServerContext = $webinfo(\"WEBSERVERCONTEXT\") \n getitem/id Session, WebServerContext, \"SESSION\" \n UserContext = \"\" \n activate \"USYSSTAT\".GetState(Session, $instancename, UserContext) \n getlistitems/id /component UserContext\nend; preActivate</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nyx1665702540047.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$webinfo (\"WebServerContext\")</a><p>The WebServerContext topic contains an associative list of properties that provide state information about the Uniface Server and the context in which it is running.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksm1665702577277.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancename</a><p>Return the name of the current component instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528418\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528418\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GetState Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Retrieves information to the USTATE table. \"USYSSTAT\".GetState ( SesstionId , $instancename , SessionData ) Table 1. Parameters Parameter Type Direction Value SesstionId string IN Generated by Uniface, and accessible using $webinfo(\"WEBSERVERCONTEXT\"), SESSION . $instancename string IN Name of the server page component instance, returned by $instancename . SessionData string OUT Uniface list of state information. Returns Uniface list of state information. Example: GetState The default code of the preActivate trigger of dynamic and static server pages activates the GetState operation and use the information returned in SessionData to set component variables to restore the server page state: Explain this code trigger preActivate variables string WebServerContext, Session, UserContext endvariables WebServerContext = $webinfo(\"WEBSERVERCONTEXT\") getitem/id Session, WebServerContext, \"SESSION\" UserContext = \"\" activate \"USYSSTAT\".GetState(Session, $instancename, UserContext) getlistitems/id /component UserContext end; preActivate Copy Related Links $webinfo (\"WebServerContext\") The WebServerContext topic contains an associative list of properties that provide state information about the Uniface Server and the context in which it is running. $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}